<div class="thumbinner" style="width:250px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Talmudtrial.jpg" class="image" title="This portrays the story of a disputation between Saint Dominic and the Cathars (Albigensians), in which the books of both were thrown on a fire and St. Dominic's books were miraculously preserved from the flames. Painting by Pedro Berruguete"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/f/fe/Talmudtrial.jpg" width="248" height="360" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
